      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="C%C3%B3mo-terminar-las-animaciones">Cómo terminar las animaciones<a class="anchor-link" href="#C%C3%B3mo-terminar-las-animaciones"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 90" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Si tenemos una animación que solo se ejecuta una vez, por ejemplo, que la bola azul se desplace hacia la derecha, cuando termine la animación irá de golpe a su posición inicial. Para evitar esto se puede usar <code>animation-fill-mode: forwards</code></p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nc">pulser</span><span class="p">::</span><span class="nd">after</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">content</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">''</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">position</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">absolute</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">width</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">height</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">top</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">left</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">background-color</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">blue</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">border-radius</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">50</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">z-index</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">-1</span><span class="p">;</span>
      
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">animation-name</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">mover</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">animation-duration</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="kt">s</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">animation-timing-function</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">linear</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">animation-direction</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">alternate</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">animation-fill-mode</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">forwards</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      </pre></div>
      <p>De esta manera, cuando termine la animación, la bola azul se quedará en la posición final</p>
      <p>Si en vez de <code>forwards</code> ponemos <code>backwards</code> la animación empezará desde el estado final</p>
      <p>Si ponemos <code>both</code> la animación empezará desde el estado final y terminará en el estado final</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Todo-en-una-l%C3%ADnea">Todo en una línea<a class="anchor-link" href="#Todo-en-una-l%C3%ADnea"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 91" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Tenemos un montón de propiedades (<code>animation-name</code> <code>animation-duration</code>, <code>animation-timing-function</code>, <code>animation-direction</code>, <code>animation-fill-mode</code>), pero se pueden poner todas en una línea. Todo lo anterior se podría poner así</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nc">pulser</span><span class="p">::</span><span class="nd">after</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">content</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">''</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">position</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">absolute</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">width</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">height</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">top</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">left</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">background-color</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">blue</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">border-radius</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">50</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">z-index</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">-1</span><span class="p">;</span>
      
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">animation</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">mover</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="kt">s</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">linear</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">alternate</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">forwards</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      </pre></div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Podemos crear varias animaciones</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nc">pulser</span><span class="p">::</span><span class="nd">after</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">content</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">''</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">position</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">absolute</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">width</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">height</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">top</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">left</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">background-color</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">blue</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">border-radius</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">50</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">z-index</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">-1</span><span class="p">;</span>
      
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">animation</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span>
      <span class="w">        </span><span class="n">mover</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="kt">s</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">linear</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">alternate</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">forwards</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="w">        </span><span class="n">agrandar</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="kt">s</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">linear</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="kt">s</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">both</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      </pre></div>
      <p>Pero como no existe la animación <code>agrandar</code> la creamos con keyframes</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="p">@</span><span class="k">keyframes</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nt">agrandar</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">0</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">        </span><span class="k">transform</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">scale</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">25</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">        </span><span class="k">transform</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">scale</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mf">1.5</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">50</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">        </span><span class="k">transform</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">scale</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">75</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">        </span><span class="k">transform</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">scale</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mf">1.6</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">100</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">        </span><span class="k">transform</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">scale</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      <span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      </pre></div>
      <p>Se va a reproducir una detrás de la otra, porque a agrandar se le ha puesto un delay de 2 segundos, que es lo que dura la primera animación, pero si queremos que sea al mismo tiempo, hay que quitar el delay</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nc">pulser</span><span class="p">::</span><span class="nd">after</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">content</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">''</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">position</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">absolute</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">width</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">height</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">100</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span>
